Package com.zorben.dns.rrdef.rdata

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    A
    Parses and stores ResourceRecord Internet Address data.
    CName
    Parses and stores ResourceRecord Canonical Name data.
    HInfo
    Parses and stores data pertaining to the information about a specific host.
    Mx
    Parses and stores data pertaining to the information about a specific host.
    Ns
    Parses and stores data pertaining to the name server authority.
    Ptr
    Parses and stores data pertaining to a domain pointer.
    RData
    Abstract structure for how ResourceRecord data should be stored and parsed.
    RDataFactory
    A static factory class for generating RData objects given the appropriate type.
    Soa
    Parses and stores data pertaining to the start of authority record.
    Txt
    Parses and stores data pertaining to the text data record.
    Wks
    Parses and stores data pertaining to the well known services record.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RDataNotSupportedException
    An exception for indicating that an RData that is trying to be constructed is unsupported.
